Text: Good Morningthere Heres my personal email addresswork is Thanks for the so called email yesterday Ha Actually I will check again when I get to work this morning Anyway hope you got all your songs downloaded last night and got a good nights sleep No more cramps for me last night I was very excited Have a great day at work and I will talk with you a little later Also I will find out what the definite plans are for Saturday night Like I said last night the whole little birthday party may never come around We may have to be creative on our own

HelloTonightis my heartfelt and meaningful email I have been waiting all day So what time are you planning on leaving work I am leaving here at and heading over to Steve and Ginas to change and walk their dog I have already taken Sophie over there That way I dont have to go home and then come back all the way over here Do you want to come over to Steve and Ginas or do you want me to come by and pick you up Hope you are having a good day Talk with you soon

Rememberingthere Hope your having a good day Just got off the phone with TammiSHE REMEMBERS Conversation started off kind of dancing around the issue and then we ended up just busting out laughing and ended the phone call still laughing Just thought I would let you know that and say hello
Checking Inchecking in to see how your are doing after your adventure to the th floor

Re Checking Inproblem about bringing it upbut you can kind of see where my mind goes when you ask something like that I have no problem talking with you about anything but never want to have the feeling that you are still working on correcting something else and in the end I would be the one looking stupid Make sense Im glad that you did what you needed to Actually I dont think I have moved my body from my chair this entire day except to go from one accounting office to another Actually I have been listening to the Beach CD again and that has kept me calm Very soothing music wellmost of itkind of like Enya I like to listen to stuff like that on days like these Keeps me calm I am actually waiting for my lunch to get here Some people went out and Judi and I are having them bring us something back I am ready for a little break Maybe I will head down to the sales dept now Wish me luck Should be quite humorous if she is there
Re Checking Inmy goshI forgot to tell youI cant make it next Saturday I thought I had told you
Re Checking Inkidding Im excitedI think it will be fun

Re Checking InI would get that other one off really fast before you wanted to call and kill me I am so funnyI just dont know what to do with myself Anyway I was downstairs a little bit ago and I could not do my hello She was on the phone the entire time Oh well theres always tomorrow By the way picked up the picture of you and I in the suite Its actually a really cute picture

FYIto let you know The Happy Hour has been changed to Little Woodrows They think it might rain Just wanted to let you know so that you could tell Eric Wouldnt want them to be hanging out at the West Alabama Ice House and we never show up

Re FYII actually got in around and it has been a very productive day I am leaving here in about minutes and I should be back around Cuts off a big portion of my day I am hoping that I will not have to stay too late tonight I have been kicking buttbut not bothering with the names Are they really that important Ha How is your day going

Re FYIyou timed that pretty good Just walked back in about minutes ago I am thinking that I will be here at least until pm I will then run home and walk Sophie and probably be able to either come by your place or just meet you at Little Woodrows by How does that work for your schedule What are you planning on doing after work That Cheeseburger sounds good I had a cold Grilled Ham and Cheese They ordered it before I left for my appt and then it had ben sitting here for about an hour before I got ot eat Yum Yum Kitty

Hands and Feetknow that you have been sitting there thinking about this since we talked lastmy hands and toes look so pretty Just thought I would give you that mental picture Anyway I should be home around If you would like to come over and see my toes you are more than welcome to

Re FW Come on feel the noiseyour message on the work email but then decided to get that out of my system Dont want anyone at corporate reading how I was in your bed last night Ha I am glad that you are recognizing exactly how cool I actually am Bad grammar on that line Miss Barbara is doing good today It has been a semislow day Kind of working at my own pace and not feeling in a rush to have anything completed It has actually been kind of nice not to be on a time crunch Went out to lunch with Renee and just got back a little bit ago I think that she was a little upset with me Her boss was asking me what I was doing for lunch and I told her that I was going with Renee She think looked like a sad puppy dog wanting to go with us and I invited herRenee was not real happy with that move Oh well it was good to catch up with someone new Sounds like you are about to loose it at workyou are quoting movie lines again Sorry to hear that you are so busy Does this mean that you will be putting in some extra hours this week When does the guy your helping out get back from skiing Hope you get a little relief from work soonhave fun

Re FW Come on feel the noise Cc I recall from the other nightI asked you all to consider me for the band one more time and there seemed to be a bunch of hem and hawing In my negotiations with Quiet Riot I have discovered that I am a hot commodity and many bands will be seeking me for their lead singer position I have even heard that more recent bands I cannot give out those names at this time have even considered asking their current lead singers to step down to a back up singer position I am sorry that our relationship has deteriorated over this one incident I tried to be fair from the beginningbut you all wanted to make sure that you created an all boys band However I am still hoping that we can resolve this issue I cannot say that my asking price will be the same given my recent brush with fame Sometimes in life we make the wrong decision and I am hoping that Monkey Pump will not make a mistake here However if Monkey Pump decides not to give me the chance to increase their potential of success I promise to still appear on VH and I promise to not say anything about the band

Heythere Just wanted to see if you got to work okay Guess who was up in our studios this morning Yep you guessed it Deblah Morgan She is actually a really young singer and she is more on the Hip Hop side of the music business Anyway I actually would have never known who she was unless someone had told me So what are you thinking about tonight Do you want to see if Eric and Jenn and David and whoever else want to meet downtown at Salintes Also were you being serious about China I really would consider it but I need to get more details about dates etc I actually think that would be so much fun Now youre sitting there saying crap why did I bring that upI was just kidding around

Re HeyMorgan She is really big in the Hip Hop world Come onget with the times here Gerald I am going to try and get out of here around I need to go get my car washed etc I am supposed to hear from Susie about that time She will then let me know what time she is going to be downtown I hope you will come along even if no one else wants to join in I know that a lot of people from work are going to be out and about tonight too You know we actually need to start spending time together outside of the alcohol At least a little earlier than at night I really dont even know if I like you Ha Ha Well I looked at my work schedule and those dates should work I just need to talk to Judi We will be in the middle of month end but I am thinking that everything could be finished by that time Ill talk with you in a little bit

Good Morningthere What time did you make it into work this morning Did you get in any traffic going home I always come back opposite of traffic and didnt know if you have any problems Anyway just wanted to say hello and say thanks for coming over last night Hope you were able to sleep soundly

Re Hey Barbarathere Sounds like someone decided to remain in bed for a little longer this morning I was actually running really late myself I didnt get in until close to Not what I was planning on doing this morning I have been working on a daily revenue report all morning trying to make sure that it goes out with the correct information Dont want to have another day like yesterday So sounds like you a crazy day has already started for you Good luck Hope you dont have to work too late tonight By the way what time are you coming over tonight Thought I would be the one to ask Ha Have a good morningjust tell all those clients that youll get the stuff to them on your own time and they can just sir back and relax
Re HeyI feel badI would have invited you to the movies but I thought you were planning your workout

Navy Seal PT Coursegroup of us are going to start a Navy Seal Training Program on April nd It runs for weeks and starts at am The cost is Just wanted to see if any of you were interested in this program You can visit their website for more information on the courses sealptcoursecom Just let me know if your interested

Just figured outwas looking through some old emails and realized that Scott forwarded me the same email that he sent to Reneethe one that I forwarded to you to show you I guess it really wasnt meant just for her I feel so sorry for her at this moment When she got that email she called and told me that she had just received the sweetest email from Scott Well I guess several people did

Re Helphave Michelle Trimm sitting in my office right now and she just explained to me that David is going to be meeting her out at Have A Nice Day Cafe this evening after he works out So looks like you will need to join me there this evening You might want to be there to keep me from my jealousy

Tomorrowthere Just heard from some people downstairs that it is probably going to be raining tomorrow Thats a good thing If the games are cancelled then I will be able to make it downtown by Keep your fingers crossed
Dont Forgetthere Dont let me forget tonight to take home those videos I need to return them tomorrow I think that means that we are going to have to watch Dr T and The Women Sorry

Re Dont Forgetdidnt go during lunch I had other errands that I needed to run I am planning on going in the morning One more thing for your list of things to dodont let me forget my purse again How is your day going

Chinathere How are you feeling I was looking on the Northwest Airlines website for flights to China I am thinking that we need to act on this pretty soon in order to get a good rate So far I have found the flights that Cathy was talking about They are approx She had stated that she heard that the price was going to go up to after the first of the month Anyway what do you think we should do Can you maybe talk with Eric today or we can wait and talk to them this evening and try and figure things out

Larry and Mia Stephenson Jr Email Subject FW Tech Problems Date Mon Nov ReturnReceiptTo MIMEVersion ContentType textplain charsetusascii XMailer Unknown No Version Dear Tech Support Last year I upgraded from Boyfriend to Husband and noticed a slow down in the performance of the flower and jewelry applications that had operated flawlessly under the Boyfriend system In addition Husband uninstalled many other valuable programs such as Romance but installed undesirable programs such as NFL NBA and NHL Conversation also no longer runs and Housecleaning simply crashes the system Ive tried running Nagging to fix these problems but to no avail What can I do Signed Desperate Dear Desperate First keep in mind that Boyfriend was an entertainment package while Husband is an operating system Try to enter the command CI THOUGHT YOU LOVED ME and install Tears Husband should then automatically run the applications Guilt and Flowers But remember overuse can cause Husband to default to such background applications as Grumpy Silence Happy Hour or Beer Please remember that Beer is a very bad program that will create SnoringLoudlyWAV files DO NOT install MotherInLaw or reinstall another Boyfriend program These are not supported applications and will crash Husband It could also potentially cause Husband to default to the program Girlfriend which runs in the background and has been known to introduce potentially serious viruses into the Operating System In summary Husband is a great program but it does have a limited memory and cant learn new applications quickly You might consider buying additional software to enhance his system performance I personally recommend Hot Food and Single Malt Scotch combined with such applications as Boob Job D and that old standbyLingerie which have both been credited with improved performance of his hardware Good Luck Tech Support
